		<mp_title>Melis Cms Slider</mp_title>
		<mp_subtitle>The module that brings a full slider system to your website.</mp_subtitle>
		<mp_description>
			MelisCmsSlider is the Slider module of Melis Platform.<br />
			The module comes with a tool that allows user to manage the list of sliders and their properties, their images and their subtitles.<br />
			MelisCmsSlider also brings a plugin to be used on pages with drag'n'drop.<br />
